trans-unit.source: Contains activities to be executed by the workflow runtime in an exception handling block.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder aktiviteter som utføres av kjøretiden arbeidsflyten i en unntaksbehandling-blokk.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the TryCatch class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av klassen TryCatch.

trans-unit.source: The collection of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Catch" name="Catch" href=""></xref> elements to be checked when the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch.Try*> activity throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen av <xref uid="langword_csharp_Catch" name="Catch" href=""> </xref> elementer som skal kontrolleres når den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch.Try*>aktiviteten oppstår det et unntak.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch.Try*>

trans-unit.source: Catches are evaluated in the order in which they are added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Fanger inn evalueres i rekkefølgen som de legges til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: If an exact match for the exception type is found, the matching <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch> activity is executed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis et nøyaktig samsvar for unntakstypen blir funnet, den tilsvarende <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch>aktiviteten er utført.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch>

trans-unit.source: If no exact match is found, the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch> with the closest matching <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch.ExceptionType%2A> is executed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen nøyaktige treff, den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch>med en samsvarende <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch.ExceptionType%2A>er utført.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch.ExceptionType%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.Catch>

trans-unit.source: The activity to be executed when the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch.Try*> and any necessary activities in the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch.Catches*> collection complete execution.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet som skal utføres når den <> </> *> og alle nødvendige aktiviteter i den <> </> *> samlingen fullstendig utførelse.

trans-unit.source: The activity that represents the Finally logic.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet som representerer den til slutt logic.

trans-unit.source: The activity first executed when the <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch"></xref> executes.
trans-unit.target: Aktiviteten først utføres når den <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.TryCatch"> </xref> utfører.
